This is GLOST, the Greedy Launcher Of Small Tasks. 

== Requirements ==

MPI

== Compil & Install ==

edit the Makefile.
$ make

== Example ==

see the scripts in directory examples/

== Documentation ==

* see ./glost_launch -h
* see ./glost_filter -h
* see ./glost_bcast

